OL,3,CFrom ATV to ITV: Blue Plaques mark 70
OL,4,Cyears of iconic television
OL,6,FBlue plaques have been unveiled to
OL,7,Fcelebrate ATV and ITV Central's
OL,8,Fcontribution to broadcasting.
OL,10,FThe event unveiling the plaques was
OL,11,Fattended by some of the stars of ITV
OL,12,FNews Central's 70 years on our
OL,13,Fscreens, including Chris Tarrant of
OL,14,FTISWAS, Sue Hanson of Crossroads and
OL,15,FBob Warman, ITV News Central's longest
OL,16,Fserving presenter.
OL,18,FThe two plaques were put up on the
OL,19,Fformer ATV building in Aston, which is
OL,20,Fnow part of the Crowne Plaza Hotel.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G1/4
