OL,3,CFrom ATV to ITV: Blue Plaques mark 70
OL,4,Cyears of iconic television
OL,6,FThey read: Alpha Television 1956-1968
OL,7,F"The Birthplaces of ITV in the
OL,8,FMidlands created by ABC and ATV, it
OL,9,Fbrought regional broadcasting to life.
OL,10,FHome of orgional programmes and a
OL,11,Fpioneer in Birmingham television
OL,12,Fhistory."
OL,14,FATV Centre, Central TV Studios 1969-
OL,15,F1997 "Purpose-built for colour
OL,16,Fbroadcasting and the creative heart of
OL,17,FITV in the Midlands. Producing iconic
OL,18,Fprogrammes, regional news and sport.
OL,19,FNurturing young talent through the
OL,20,FJunior TV Workshop."
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G2/4
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
