OL,3,CFrom ATV to ITV: Blue Plaques mark 70
OL,4,Cyears of iconic television
OL,6,FAlpha Television was made to contrast
OL,7,Fwith the BBC, giving people TV that
OL,8,Frepresented them.
OL,10,FLord Grade, the former ATV Controller,
OL,11,Fsaid, "Suddenly television was
OL,12,Frecognising that there were people
OL,13,Foutside of London."
OL,15,FMike Prince, former continuity
OL,16,Fannouncer on ATV, said, "It was
OL,17,Fdifferent to what the BBC was
OL,18,Foffering... It was really quite
OL,19,Fexciting, people were being different".
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G3/4
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
