PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F373A1777719769
OL,3,CFrom ATV to ITV: Blue Plaques mark 70
OL,4,Cyears of iconic television
OL,6,FProgrammes like "Lunch Box" and
OL,7,F"Tigger and Tucker" were widely
OL,8,Fpopular. The latter gained more than
OL,9,F700,000 young fans.
OL,11,FThe plaques from the Birmingham Civic
OL,12,FSociety are dotted around the city to
OL,13,Fmark sites of historic or cultural
OL,14,Fimportance.
OL,16,FReporting History sees journalists
OL,17,Fjoin News At Ten anchor Tom Bradby to
OL,18,Frevisit their remarkable on-the-day
OL,19,Freports of the defining events of the
OL,20,Fmodern age. Listen to the episodes
OL,21,Fbelow...
